{"tid":1782384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家黎講，Save HK個facebook group係幾值得留意","createTime":"2019-12-14T02:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T05:46:59.000Z","uid":66260,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"de327bef4421b0c63a5de21c440e816ec1d9016b","tid":1782384,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:10:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/393490971355994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F393490971355994&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=0392ddc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/393490971355994</a><br />\n<br />\n用假acc join左幾個藍屍group, 發現普遍藍屍都係冇邏輯低學歷盲撐政府，呢樣唔使多講<br />\n唯獨呢個叫Save HK既group比較特別，反送中開始後先成立，幾個月已經有十幾萬人join左，仲多過 支持香港警察 之類傳統撐警page<br />\n入面藍屍平均智商比一般撐警page高，識得自動忽略分化post, 識得分邊啲係content farm假新聞<br />\n圍爐性質好強，只要喺內文吹奏警甴必定有過千回應<br />\n值得一提係入面有極多警甴成員或警甴家屬水炮車，呢類人出post分分鐘呃到成千上萬個like同留言<br />\n<br />\nadmin係呢個人<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/rockbottom888?groupid=393490971355994&amp;fref=gm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Frockbottom888%3Fgroupid%3D393490971355994%26fref%3Dgm&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=b58cc0b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/rockbottom888?groupid=393490971355994&amp;fref=gm</a><br />\n仲有呢個page<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/SaveHKOfficial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FSaveHKOfficial%2F&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=e43869e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/SaveHKOfficial/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有能力請咁多人拍片，應該背後有大機構水喉照住"},{"pid":"72b4228f83d0fb5ddbc07e1f4411653ab523403e","tid":1782384,"uid":70679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:14:07.000Z","msg":"我舉報左&hellip;&hellip;但可能無乜用"},{"pid":"196ab571b3009e5eb5dff791c88cab276e3927fb","tid":178